      "description": "Offering a driver-spec 2004 BMW M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six and a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. This chassis has been properly sorted with reinforced rear subframe mounting points and a comprehensive VANOS system refresh to ensure optimal variable valve timing. The mechanical LSD provides predictable lock-up under load, while the individual throttle bodies offer the razor-sharp induction response this platform is famous for. Recent service includes a cooling system overhaul and fresh bushings to maintain suspension kinematics. It\u2019s an honest, mechanically robust example built for the purist.",
